<----- grubb.ly 
         mobile food discovery ----->

A dynamic food truck discovery engine. Provides near real-time, visual 
    map points of local, twittering food trucks.	 

Features:
  - Hosted in the Google App Engine
  - OAuth Twitter integration
  - @anywhere tweet function
  - Google Maps integration


In Progress:
  - Tweet crawler
  - cron
  - CSS upgrade, additional browser support (Tested only in Chrome)

Install Directions:
  -  In app.py uncomment CONSUMER_KEY, CONSUMER_SECRET and CALLBACK_URL and 
     replace with your own designated app key, secret and callback.  
